cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.GT, cs.AL, cs.NE 

This paper deals with load balancing algorithms, which are commonly studied in the distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. It also involves game theory (cs.GT) in terms of optimizing the balance of the load, and algorithms (cs.AL) and network economics (cs.NE) in terms of designing a decentralized and efficient algorithm.
